    "notes": "<h3>Abilities</h3><ul><li><strong>Double Tap</strong>: The Tir Ghost can use a Complex Action to attack with their Ares Light Fire 75 pistol to increase their attack’s DV by 1.</li><li><strong>Impossible to Kill</strong>: Once per fight, when the Tir Ghost is hit by an attack (including AOE attacks), they can make the attack miss instead.</li><li><strong>Pinning Shot</strong>: When attacking with a shuriken, the Tir Ghost can use the Pinning Shot Weapons Talent.</li></ul><h3>Traits</h3><ul><li><strong>Vision Enhancements</strong>: Flare Compensation, Low-</li><li><strong>Light, Thermographic, Vision Magnification</strong>: </li><li><strong>Mash the Trigger</strong>: The Tir Ghost does not suffer</li><li><strong>recoil penalties.</strong>: </li><li><strong>Lethal Assassin</strong>: If the Tir Ghost has Leverage on an</li><li><strong>attack test, they can reroll 1 Crit Die and must use the</strong>: </li><li><strong>new result.</strong>: </li></ul>",
